{"tid":1721580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"以大學作為聚腳點轉守為攻","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:36:42.000Z","uid":40663,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"527b2088662f7e0912a8058c4b2df46bc10cdf06","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"可能已經有好多手足講過<br />\n政府係用返當年雨革招數<br />\n將所謂嘅「重要據點」犧牲俾我地一兩個月<br />\n期間不斷派糖、激起民怨、民鬥民，去冷處理定性做示威區嘅大學範圍<br />\n簡單嚟講：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地：精神崩緊、心靈有個寄託覺得我地示威緊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢地：養精蓄銳、賺民心、少量兵已經可以令大家躁動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但或者我地可以參考烏克蘭嗰邊嘅手法？</span></span></strong><br />\n好似中大依家咁<br />\n雖然入面慢慢形成咗自己一套嘅機制，有糧有醫護站有武器<br />\n但感覺就似「守城」，我地唔郁，佢地每個出入口放10隻狗就可以block撚晒我地<br />\n<br />\n我建議黎緊嘅行動，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要主動出擊</span></strong></span><br />\n如果有大學據點喺附近<br />\n請所有人<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先將物資同自己搬到大學</span></span></strong><br />\n之後喺大學範圍聚人，再出擊，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以大學作為據點去守點</span></span></strong><br />\n例如浸大城大為例，其實包括咗勁撚多區<br />\n好似黃大仙區、九龍城區、深水埗區<br />\n手足應該要比依家多幾十倍<br />\n<br />\n至於出擊地點，可以係一直久攻不下嘅龍翔道，或者窩打老道等等<br />\n附近政府建築物、隧道亦可以係目標<br />\n<br />\n可能我嘅睇法好狹窄，一定有完善嘅空間<br />\n但我覺得<br />\n再守落去，我地一定唔會贏<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港冇嘢可以再守架喇</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"aec19e048e466cd5dbf46a0a684b994608b777f7","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ccb5118282658e725bde3bf8242c3df55b035971","tid":1721580,"uid":308740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"急!!!!!!!!葵涌邨要人要記者!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721248</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\npush"},{"pid":"1e846a1a586ba8ab8d3d78f4c6536612e27013ea","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bffef2271ea6670e4b2edab2d42b266d47d564cb","tid":1721580,"uid":161504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!"},{"pid":"4b82aa59220c74b194d68fcbd5f68447141f4a48","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b96296bc4c466ec3f4d6b5b2408af595bf9f015","tid":1721580,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"要塞要攻"},{"pid":"6d2bc36c20f1dbe146e30a590af819e686884c32","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"897ff3582edb1a9f3c01bc5beb38d581de1ad0d3","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dafa00306c904484f67513d24d96fc45dbbb4a42","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df5d077b4f023fec67ea0af74780d7153b6d2e8b","tid":1721580,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"003e1bffa24d0d0f28cc907b903899f3b6193ac1","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"0db2a114b5290eb3c7e6fa6e1deb4ebd058e2a22","tid":1721580,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89a1c89291584ef90242be0f08bf44f268fa8ed7","tid":1721580,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:55:16.00